{
  "stem": "20035.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, these guys had rubber boots all the way around, you know, like a fisherman has it all the way to the hip, and rubber gloves all the way to the shoulder and masks and God knows what.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And suddenly came with a pump and they started to spray something on us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My thinking was at that time that these guys had-- these guys have seen the movie, but they don't know what real life is, because I don't need baby powder.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But within seconds, I realized what they did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't know what it was, but within seconds, I had no more lice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Before that, we were infected by millions of those lice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Later on found out what they sprayed, it was DDT.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, thank goodness today's world doesn't use DDT.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But DDT in seconds killed all the lice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was taken by these Red Cross people on a stretcher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was put on a stretcher and was taken into a school building right there, which became some kind of a hospital or whatever you want to call it, the Red Cross shelter.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Neubrandenburg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh my goodness.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A long, long time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would like to tell you that according to records, I was 32 kilos. 32 kilos is roughly 70 pounds.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes in June, July, they taught me how to walk, how to stand up and walk, because I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a tough time to find even the skin available, injections.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I know The vein they had no problem to find, but they couldn't find anything in the back or anything in the arm or skin sometimes for days.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started to bring called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I stayed there sometimes in September, October.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
